{"tid":2414314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始向外媒表示：科興疫苗沒受共產黨施壓","createTime":"2021-02-19T10:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T17:56:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"422aafdbd4b640f761744f35818901770454c668","tid":2414314,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"陳肇始：沒有將任何新冠疫苗政治化<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始接受外電訪問時表示，當局無降低審批科興疫苗的標準，北京亦沒有施壓，要求特區政府批准使用疫苗，強調疫苗是本港控制疫情的希望，政府沒有將任何新冠疫苗政治化，亦不應該將疫苗接種過程政治化。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨天批准內地科興疫苗緊急使用，最快下星期五為5類優先群組免費接種。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2379704&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=984f8d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2379704</a>"},{"pid":"7910b9d8b052166c673f3b38e455165e74ead985","tid":2414314,"uid":58841,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"即係有啦"},{"pid":"84533d0eec71840546679b04b110915138a4f69b","tid":2414314,"uid":127575,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7910b9d8b052166c673f3b38e455165e74ead985","tid":2414314,"uid":58841,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"即係有啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"即係有啦 x2"},{"pid":"4b2a37fbb6fe756a890d8ede878024128e7c0eec","tid":2414314,"uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4be4c08a814af7b3446d790f949ee801f416af","tid":2414314,"uid":13663,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d69mP3M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd69mP3M.gif&h=00717d99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eb6e8d559220fce8aa9